### Real-Life Example:
Think of this architecture as a SMART CITY MONITORING SYSTEM:

DATA SOURCES:
- Traffic sensors (IoT)
- Weather stations (Telegraf)
- Transit systems (Kinesis)
- Power grid (Prometheus)

PROCESSING:
- Lambda cleans and transforms
- Timestream stores everything
